Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:25.81,Default,NTP,100,0,0,,{\an7\p1\1a&HFF&\c&HCDCDCD&\pos(16,12)}m 0 0 l 650 0 l 650 234 l 0 234
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:25.81,Default,NTP,170,0,0,,{\an7\fs60}无限制居住许可证
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:25.81,Default,NTP,340,0,0,,{\an7\fs60}谷风长道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:25.81,Default,NTP,200,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}希德尼娅军卫人队西4管辖区\N下属高级操纵士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}兹证明以上人物破例获准居住于\N包括外周壁居住特别区内的区域
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:25.81,Default,NTP,300,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}出航纪元1010年4月\N希德尼娅军总司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…无限制居住许可证！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.18,0:10:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是第一次带人去看外周壁的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要再找找配线图
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过真羡慕你啊 居然能住在外周壁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:10:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,操纵士们都必须住在干线轨道机关附近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这里怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是老房子了 不过有这么多旧管线绕来绕去的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…这样好像有点不太好钻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有更靠东一点的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔 那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.99,0:11:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这间怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这里好像不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.77,0:11:40.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是缬啊 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近休假经常报销 都抽不出时间来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.74,0:11:52.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔你有进到什么好货吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这难不成是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引力子放射线发射装置啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理论上最强的武器…！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 是自制的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.84,0:12:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我小时候在「架空武器大全」里见过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:19.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「这种武器无坚不摧！」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:23.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那本书我到现在都还留着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过话说回来 还真是好怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能喜欢真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天还让你陪我直接过去看 真是太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.75,0:12:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里 能看到漂亮的管线我也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:49.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里是住房管理局…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啧 大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.64,0:13:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回得挺早嘛 还好把钥匙给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.06,0:13:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要直接住下…嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,配线图？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我今天去看了看要搬过去的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？啊 是 是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:33.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是我今天看的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是䌷的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 这可是外周壁的房子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.07,0:13:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要不要也一起搬过去？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 前提是你愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 什么叫前提是我愿意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.41,0:13:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里可是外周壁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可能是能搞到批准
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是像我这样的普通操纵士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不能住这种地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…没 没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面写着允许找一个人同住的…你看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 伊札那？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.77,0:14:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.27,0:14:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来是想先跟你商量的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是今天突然有空了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.03,0:14:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是无所谓 跟你一起搬过去也行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.63,0:14:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.88,0:14:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这离车站也太远了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 建筑后面就有通往军事区的升降轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个好地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫䌷过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊札那 先屏住气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.09,0:15:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷说管线里灰尘很多 所以她准备加个压
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.77,0:15:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正本来也准备要打扫了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了灰尘之外没什么问题了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.96,0:15:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 都没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.13,0:16:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面也很宽敞 来这里的路上挺舒适的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风先生 你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.05,0:16:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去没什么精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.03,0:16:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷…你还没睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我其实不睡也没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然想睡也能睡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是个怪胎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.28,0:16:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它贴在后面的墙上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这不是锹形虫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘 你声音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊札那大概已经睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我可以摸摸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:16:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:16:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过要轻点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.86,0:17:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是第一次见到活的锹形虫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.15,0:17:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长得好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.46,0:17:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我本来就打算放了它的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于锹形虫来说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们肯定只是无法交流的可怕的捕食者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 或许是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.75,0:17:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许只是彼此太过不同 不知道该怎样正确地交流而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.55,0:17:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星白…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 谷风先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都这么晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.70,0:17:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:17:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那再见了 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和谷风先生一起睡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.25,0:18:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.73,0:18:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浮游小行星正通过本舰附近
